<p><strong>What makes content citable by AI:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Clear definitions in the first 2 sentences of each section</li>
<li>Original statistics, benchmarks, or frameworks (not just reworded competitor content)</li>
<li>Numbered steps that AI can extract as a direct answer</li>
